File:JiuJiang Bridge.jpg|The [[Jiujiang Yangtze River Bridge]], an arch bridge, was completed in 1992.
File:Yichang Yangtze Highway Bridge 3.jpg|The [[Yichang Bridge|Yichang Yangtze Highway Bridge]], a [[suspension bridge]] near the Gezhouba Dam lock, was completed in 1996.
File:Sutong Bridge.jpg|The [[Sutong Bridge|Sutong Yangtze River Bridge]], between [[Nantong]] and [[Suzhou]], was one of the longest [[cable-stayed bridges]] in the world when it was completed in 2008.
