==Dams==
[[File:Three Gorges dam.jpg|thumb|left|The Three Gorges Dam in 2006]]
[[File:Yangtze longitudinal profile upstream.JPG|thumb|right|Diagram showing dams planned for the upper reaches of the Yangtze River]]
As of 2007, there are two dams built on the Yangtze river: [[Three Gorges Dam]] and [[Gezhouba Dam]]. Several dams are being constructed on the upper portion of the river, the [[Jinsha River]].

==Tributaries==
[[Image:Yangzi river ship yard on river bank.jpg|thumb|right|A shipyard on the banks of the Yangtze building commercial river freight boats]]
The Yangtze River has over 700 [[tributaries]]. The major tributaries (listed from upstream to downstream) with the locations of where they join the Yangtze are:
