*[[Yuan River]]
*[[Lishui River]]
*[[Zi River]]
*[[Xiang River]] ([[Yueyang]], Hunan)
*[[Han River (Hanshui)|Han River]] ([[Wuhan]], Hubei)
*[[Gan River (Jiangxi)|Gan River]] (near [[Jiujiang]], Jiangxi Province.)
